    "title": "FitOn Holdings Services is Hiring: Floor Manager (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "FitOn Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Floor Manager at our Tiruchirappalli location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout FitOn Holdings Services:\nFitOn Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FitOn Holdings Services!",
